    "system_start_date": "2026-03-16",
    "week_number_logic": "week_number is determined by counting full weeks since system_start_date (2026-03-16). week_number = ((floor(days_since_start / 7)) % 2 == 0) ? 1 : 2. So weeks 0,2,4... from start = Week 1; weeks 1,3,5... = Week 2. The first 7 days (Mar 16-22) = Week 1."
